SmallInvoice,is,an,invoice,servce,designed,for,small,and,medium,sized,businesses,as,well,as,freelance,workers,The,base,service,is,free,to,use,and,additional,tiers,of,service,are,available,The,SmallInvoice,API,uses,REST,calls,and,allows,users,to,perform,tasks,involving,user,accounts,and,invoices,Sample,calls,include,creating,invoices,submitting,invoices,accepting,offers,drafting,receipts,and,other,calls,An,account,is,required,with,service